main event: A witness sighted a brownish black object that looked like an airplane without wings, which disappeared in the distance.
interesting points: The witness was requested several times to complete a Form 14 but failed to do so.
The observer would not allow the investigators to take any photos.
No other similar reports were received.
The object was described as a solid, sharply outlined object that did not make any sound.
The witness estimated the object was approximately 3,000 yards away and at an altitude of 75 feet.
sighted object: brownish black object that looked like an airplane without wings
